
		      # ====================== #
		      # cmake tools repository #
		      # ====================== #

* Introduction

This directory contains a set of tools to use with the cmake build system.

* Directories

** conf

This directory contains a set of ruby functions used to run cmake cmake. They
are provided as a convenience in order to avoid to the user to set many
cmake variables by hand.

** modules

Holds cmake modules. See modules/README for further information about how to
write/use the provided modules.

